I found a likely root cause: frame ontology terms currently ingest BM25 match tokens directly, including generic stopwords and punctuation-derived fragments, which can leak noisy `frame-term:*` and F-logic term triples. I’m validating this against existing unit tests, then I’ll add deterministic term sanitization with tests.
